content:
Amazon is incentivized to make the sellers spend money on ads to get their products ranked, otherwise they just rank the copy of their own products at the top. Either way, amazon makes money, but once I figured out this system, I was able to get out of this NICKNAME cycle and then I was able to maximize my products and sell out my entire stock without spending a penny on ads.
Generate 50 nicknames to describe a situation where my amazon fba products are not being ranked by amazon's organic search algorithm.
